transcripts:
Hey there, I'd like to introduce to you the new trampoline and safety closure from Upper Bounce. This Upper Bounce set includes: 

Special rust resistant galvanized steel frame. 
Legs
Poles 
And Springs that are made to last 

Upper Bounce jumping mat is ultra durable. Its premium mesh material and stitching prevent the mat from tearing and guarantee enjoyment for years. the high quality safety pad is one inch foam. Its shock absorbent and won't absorb water, mildew or lose its shape. The high quality enclosure net ensures that you can enjoy you jumping experience knowing you are fully protected from any accident. And it has a bouncing capacity of up to 250 pounds and on the larger models, up to 330 pounds. High quality foam sleeves provide color and design to your trampoline in addition to padding and and safety net poles for added protection. Our easy assemble disassemble trampolines are especially designed to make it easy to take apart the poles protection during the winter. And it will save you from constantly replacing trampoline parts. The Upper Bounce! Looks like fun doesn't it? It is is fun, get the Upper Bounce. You heard her, get the Upper Bounce.
